Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:29.40,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Get back to where
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.50,0:22:31.07,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I once belonged, BUT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.16,0:22:34.94,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}振り向けば 風の音だけ　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.02,0:22:36.20,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Don't let me down　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.32,0:22:37.85,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Don't make me confuse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.95,0:22:42.83,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}絶望が塗り潰してく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.98,0:22:44.68,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Escape from here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.73,0:22:46.49,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}It's like a nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:49.13,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}追いかけてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:52.85,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}夢も　理想も　情熱も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.96,0:22:56.38,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}またかき消されて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:59.35,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}哀しい日々は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.53,0:23:02.94,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}いつかは終わりが來るの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:06.06,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}迷いながら　もがきながら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:11.84,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}それでも　まだあきらめたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.08,0:23:13.78,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}傷だらけでも　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:18.78,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}この手のひらに 決して消えない星がある 　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.85,0:23:22.13,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}流れて墮ちた光は今も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:25.91,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}あの場所を遠く照らしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.14,0:23:29.14,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}何度でも手を伸ばそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:32.38,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}今は描けなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:35.52,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}信じることが強さに変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.60,0:23:38.83,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}輝いてよ　Shooting STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:29.40,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Get back to where
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.50,0:22:31.07,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I once belonged, BUT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.16,0:22:34.94,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}转身遥望 只有风声　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.02,0:22:36.20,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Don't let me down　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.32,0:22:37.85,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Don't make me confuse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.95,0:22:42.83,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}将绝望掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.98,0:22:44.68,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Escape from here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.73,0:22:46.49,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}It's like a nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:49.13,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}正在追逐着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:52.85,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}梦想　理想　热情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.96,0:22:56.38,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}也全都消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:59.35,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}悲伤的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.53,0:23:02.94,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}会不会有结束之日？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:06.06,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}迷惘着 挣扎着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:11.84,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使如此 也还不想放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.08,0:23:13.78,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使伤痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:18.78,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}在手中 仍有绝不会消失的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.85,0:23:22.13,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}滑落之后 那光芒现在也 　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:25.91,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}依然远远地照耀着那里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.14,0:23:29.14,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}无数次伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:32.38,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使现在无法描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:35.52,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}信任会化为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.60,0:23:38.83,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}闪耀吧 Shooting STAR
